name: Exim - The Messenger
description:
Music: Analog synthesizer recording using Korg MS-20
Artwork: Mixed media using brush tip marker and digital animation - 2021 - gif - 452x640 - Aline Vieira @floresfeias - Part of Codex Crypto Angelus series.

It connects the human soul with conducting minerals. Exim is a personal messenger. 

Gold, copper and tin were made. In the inhabited land, the message overflowed the word. Exim, the conductor, carried the light code energy to each user as a guardian of the language.
